data.description: BUT WAIT, THERE'S MORE! Look at the 30x40, 3 stall garage with 15k lb truck lift, air compressor and 15' ceiling with office on level ground surrounded with privacy fencing. The garage has 3 - 10x10 insulated doors and shop is insulated and has 200 amp service. The yard has enough room for your camper and boat and toys, all surrounded with privacy fencing. Electric is available to keep your camper plugged in and separate clean out for your camper. The stick built utility building is 12x24 with power to store your smaller items for convenience. House is on a slab so there's no stairs to get tripped. Very nice an comfortable floor plan as you will see and with extra storage closets. The fireplace even has a gas starter for added convenience. The back yard oasis is impressive and level and grassy and surrounded with privacy fencing for added security. By the way, security cameras will stay. Part of the back patio is covered and is nice to sit outside with your morning coffee or afternoon adult beverage and on those days that you need some water rejuvenation, well there's the hot tub ready to go. This property is highly desired due to lot size and privacy. There is also room to have a flower or vegetable garden for those with a green thumb. The front yard is very nice and inviting with a little patch of woods that the deer like to bed in. Oh yes, Turtle Cove has quite the amenities to include a clubhouse with restaurant and lounge, golf course, pool, tennis courts, playground for the kiddos, resident only beaches, boat ramps, & on site security guards.
